data.description: Fantastic 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 1,466 sq ft home with large bonus room. Centrally located in Peninsula, this neat & tidy home features carpet and ceramic tile floors throughout, fresh interior paint, tile surround showers, Milgard windows, and central heat & air! Fenced backyard, storage shed, RV parking on a spacious corner lot with mature landscaping. Plus ALL appliances are included!
